      "name": "Adamancipator Risen - Tiamite",
      "effect": "1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuners\nIf you have a DARK monster in your GY: You can add 1 \"Adamancipator\" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand. When your opponent activates a monster effect on the field (Quick Effect): You can excavate the top 5 cards of your Deck, and if you do, you can return cards your opponent controls to the hand, up to the number of excavated Rock monsters, also place the excavated cards on the bottom of the Deck in any order. You can only use each effect of \"Adamancipator Risen - Tiamite\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
